---
title: Running Log
metaTitle: Running Log
tags: ['about','running']
description: A running log to track dates, distance, time, pace, heart rate, and Vo2 Max.
---
<p class="lead">Running activity tracked with a Garmin Forerunner 45, logged in Garmin Connect, and published here with Eleventy. More <a href="/notes/2021/eleventy-garmin-connect/">about the project</a>. </p>

<table class="full_width table_rwd">
  <thead>
  <tr>
    <th>When</th>
    <th>Distance</th>
    <th>Time</th>
    <th>Pace</th>
    <th>Heart Rate</th>
    <th><abbr title="volume, oxygen, maximum">VO<sub>2</sub> Max</th>
    </tr>
   </thead>
   {% for item in running.garmin.activityList %}
  {% if item.sportTypeId == "1" %}
  <tr id="{{ item.activityId }}">
    <th scope="rowgroup" {% if (item.description) or (item.favorite == true) or (item.pr == true) %}rowspan="2"{% endif %}><a href="https://connect.garmin.com/modern/activity/{{ item.activityId }}">{{ item.startTimeLocal | date("M/D/Y") }}</a><br> {{ item.startTimeLocal | date("h:mm A")}}</th>
    <td data-tblColumn="Time">{{ item.distance | miles }} mi</td>
    <td data-tblColumn="Distance">{{ item.duration | duration("mm:ss") }}</td>
    <td data-tblColumn="Pace">{{ ((item.duration)/(item.distance | miles)) | duration("m:ss") }}/mi</td>
    <td data-tblColumn="Heart Rate">{{ item.averageHR }} <acronym title="beats per minute">bpm</acronym><br> ({{ item.maxHR }}&nbsp;Max)</td>
    <td data-tblColumn="VO2 Max">{% if item.vO2MaxValue %}{{ item.vO2MaxValue }} <abbr title="volume, oxygen, maximum">VO<sub>2</sub> Max</abbr>{% endif %}</td>
  </tr>
  {% if (item.description) or (item.favorite == true) or (item.pr == true) %}<tr>
    <td colspan="5" data-tblColumn="Description">
      <p>{% if item.description %}{{ item.description }} {% endif %}
      {% if item.favorite == true %}‚≠ê Marked as one of my favorites. {% endif %}
      {% if item.pr == true %}üèÜ Includes a personal record.{% endif %}</p>
    </td>
  </tr>{% endif %}
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}
</table>